title: Did U.S. Rep. Ilhan Omar Say “We Are Here to Take Over America”?
subtitle: Not only is the quote made up, it runs counter to several public statements Omar has made on the topic of being both Muslim and American.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: U.S. Rep. Ilhan Omar once said: "We are not here to be part of America. We are here to take over America."
